## Diagram — checkout to invoice

```mermaid
flowchart TD
  A[checkout-create] --> B[Validate customer payment address]
  B --> C[cart/retrieve + checkoutdata]
  C --> D[POST order/create Exotic]
  D --> E[Extract order_number]
  E --> F[pos_editorderprices optional]
  F --> G[pos_payment_insert_row per split]
  G --> H[Store pos_checkout_invoice_snapshot]
  H --> I[importSingleOrderForCheckoutWithRetry]
  I --> J{vp_orders ready?}
  J -->|yes| K[createAutoInvoiceForOrder]
  J -->|no| L[Receipt only import_status failed]
  K --> M{allocation complete?}
  M -->|final| N[Tax invoice PDF]
  M -->|partial| O[Proforma invoice]
  G --> P[checkout-receipt page]
  P --> Q[Later payments via Payments module]
  Q --> R[pos_payment_finalize_invoice_for_order]
  R --> N
```

